<p>Welcome to <strong>Lifting Library</strong>! Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal information when you use our workout tracking app.</p>

<h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> Name, email address, and password when you create an account.</li>
    <li><strong>Workout Data:</strong> Exercise details, sets, reps, weights, and progress tracking.</li>
    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device type, operating system, and app version.</li>
    <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Features accessed, time spent in the app, and interactions.</li>
    <li><strong>Optional Information:</strong> Notes, goals, or custom workout plans you enter.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Provide and improve the app’s functionality.</li>
    <li>Track workout progress and display analytics.</li>
    <li>Personalize your experience and recommendations.</li>
    <li>Maintain account security and support.</li>
    <li>Comply with legal obligations if necessary.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Data Sharing & Third Parties</h2>
<p>We <strong>do not</strong> sell your personal data. We may share data only in the following cases:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> Trusted third-party services that help operate and improve the app (e.g., cloud storage, analytics tools).</li>
    <li><strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> If required by law or to protect user safety.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data Security</h2>
<p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including encryption, secure servers, and access controls. However, no online system is 100% secure, so we recommend using a strong password and keeping your credentials private.</p>

<h2>5. Your Rights & Choices</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Access, update, or delete your account and personal data.</li>
    <li>Export your workout data upon request.</li>
    <li>Opt out of optional data collection (e.g., analytics).</li>
    <li>Request account deletion at any time.</li>
</ul>
<p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <strong>[Insert Contact Email]</strong>.</p>

<h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
<p>We retain your data as long as your account is active. If you delete your account, we will remove your data.</p>

<h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
<p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted in the app, and we encourage you to review it periodically.</p>

<h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns, please reach out to us at <strong>Support@LiftingLibrary.com</strong>.</p>

<p>By using <strong>Lifting Library</strong>, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.</p>